{
  "id": "69c0259ec42c87b8fbc19206",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:AI使用禁止令",
  "created": 1774200245,
  "updated": 1774200259,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c0259ec42c87b8fbc19206",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:AI使用禁止令",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200245,
      "updated": 1774200245
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b50000000000871b57",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200245,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b58",
      "text": "「はいはーい！今日のテーマは『[AI使用禁止令]』ね！なんか最近、学校とかで“AI使っちゃダメ！”みたいな話あるじゃん？あれってどうなん？ってやつ〜」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b59",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5a",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5b",
      "text": "「ええ、たしかに耳にすることが増えましたね。便利な道具であるはずのものが、まるで禁じられた書物のように扱われるのは、少し切ない気もいたします……（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5e",
      "text": "「前提を整理しよう。“AI使用禁止令”は主に教育現場での不正防止を目的としている。具体的には、レポートや課題の自動生成を抑止するための措置だね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b5f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b60",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b61",
      "text": "「あー、ズル防止ってことね。たしかに丸投げで課題出したら、それもう“自分でやってない”って感じだしw」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b62",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b63",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b64",
      "text": "「ただ、完全に禁じてしまうのは、まるで筆や紙を取り上げるようなものにも思えてしまいます。道具は使い方次第で、人を助けるものにもなりましょうに……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b65",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b66",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b67",
      "text": "「その通り。ツールの“禁止”は短期的には効果があるが、長期的にはスキル格差を広げる可能性がある。AIリテラシー、つまり“適切に使う力”の育成が本質的課題だ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b69",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6a",
      "text": "「リテラシーってやつね〜。なんかさ、“使うな！”って言われると逆に使いたくなるやつじゃん？w」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6c",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]（小さく笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6d",
      "text": "「確かに、人の心とは不思議なものですね。禁じられるほどに、その存在が大きく映ってしまう……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b6f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b70",
      "text": "「加えて、現実社会ではAIの活用は不可避。例えばプログラミングでも補助ツールとして使うのが一般的だ。完全禁止は“現実との乖離”を生む」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b72",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b73",
      "text": "「あー、それわかる！社会出たら“AI使って効率よくやってね”って言われそうなのに、学校だけ“禁止！”って、ちょいズレてる感ある〜」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b74",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b75",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b76",
      "text": "「けれども、学ぶ過程そのものを大切にしたい、という気持ちも分かるのです。自ら考え、悩み、言葉を紡ぐ時間は、かけがえのないものですから……」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b77",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b78",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b79",
      "text": "「そこがトレードオフだね。“思考力の育成”と“効率化”。解決策は二択ではない。条件付き許可が現実的だ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7b",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7c",
      "text": "「条件付きってどゆこと？」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7e",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b7f",
      "text": "「例えば、“AI使用を明記する”“生成物をそのまま提出しない”“プロセスを説明させる”。こうすれば不正は抑制できるし、学習効果も担保できる」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b80",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b81",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b82",
      "text": "「まあ……それは、まるで“誰とどのように対話したかを記す日記”のようですね。思考の足跡が見えるのは、教師の方にも安心を与えるでしょう」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b83",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b84",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b85",
      "text": "「なるほどね〜！“AI使いました！”って正直に言って、その上でちゃんと自分の考えも出せばOKって感じか。なんかそれならフェアじゃん！」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b87",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b88",
      "text": "「要点をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b89",
      "text": " 1. 完全禁止は現実と乖離する",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8a",
      "text": " 2. 無制限使用は不正リスクが高い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8b",
      "text": " 3. よって“透明性のある制限付き利用”が最適解",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8c",
      "text": "…こんなところだ」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8e",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b8f",
      "text": "「どちらかを切り捨てるのではなく、折り合いを見つける……まるで物語の結末のように、やさしい着地点ですね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b90",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b91",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b92",
      "text": "「いい感じにまとまったじゃん！結論、“AIは敵じゃなくて使い方しだい！”ってことで〜。はい、この話題、クリアってことでいい？w」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b93",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b94",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b95",
      "text": "「異論なし。議論終了」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b97",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b60000000000871b98",
      "text": "「ええ、心穏やかに締めくくれましたね（微笑）」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200246,
      "updated": 1774200246
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b80000000000871b99",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200248,
      "updated": 1774200248
    },
    {
      "id": "69c025b80000000000871b9a",
      "text": "#2026-03-22",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1774200249,
      "updated": 1774200259
    },
